E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Sinh-t%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A0n-nhi-d%C4%A9/poem-NLrtL8QCgNQgkrUCWjvPEA">Sinh tử nhàn nhi dĩ - 生死閑而已</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Tr%C4%A9-S%C6%A1n-c%C3%B4-th%C3%A1p/poem-OL2ohomglTMD2k8iQtpCUg">Trĩ Sơn cô tháp - 峙山孤塔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/V%E1%BA%A1n-s%E1%BB%B1-quy-nh%C6%B0/poem-fpW7euMg85Nsgj5ASUIGQQ">Vạn sự quy như - 萬事歸如</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-XV/poem-OmGFvpb1-fdvi4DgXVaDZw">Vô đề (XV) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/author-1swHDuDfqhjQRVvirtpDBQ">Phạm Kỳ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
